author: jonl
msg: Minor refactoring: added constructor that omits validation feedback parameter, made conflict resolver and upload folder into properties, moved logic from onSubmit() into protected saveFiles() method for clarity in subclasses.

author: ehillenius
msg: Upload example now has two forms that display different uses (with/ without textfields for naming) and also shows that multiple uploads are possible.
- renamed AbstractUploadForm to UploadForm to encourage direct use
- removed single handle file methods; saving of files is now only done by FileUploadForm.onSubmit
- added UploadTextField with special model UploadModel and a special validator to make working with uploads and text fields for naming those uploads easier
- put files in map instead of list
